## Data Flow

[Describe how data flows through the system]

### Example: User Request Flow
1. User sends request to API endpoint
2. Controller validates input
3. Service layer processes business logic
4. Repository layer queries database
5. Response flows back through layers
6. User receives formatted response

```
User Request
     │
     ▼
[API Layer] ──> Validate Input
     │
     ▼
[Service Layer] ──> Process Logic
     │
     ▼
[Repository Layer] ──> Query Database
     │
     ▼
[Database] ──> Return Data
     │
     ▼
[Response] ──> Format & Return
```

